From 75726ae6e9dfd416e84f0fd3d0c443a99b31a290 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Brad Larson <bradley.larson@amd.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2026 12:58:56 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 18/20] arm64: dts: amd: add Elba, Giglio and Deschutes boards

Add the devicetree sources for the AMD Pensando Elba and Giglio SoCs and
the Giglio-based Deschutes board, including PSCI and spin-table boot,
flash partitioning and secure-boot variants.

The Giglio-based Deschutes board support was added by Mushtaq Khan.

Signed-off-by: Brad Larson <bradley.larson@amd.com>
